title: Survey - Speedster/VX220
htmlContent:
Survey - Speedster/VX220

The Speedster/VX220 for MY 2003 sees the introduction of the 2.0 litre Turbo model. The Turbo model is available in addition to the 2.2 litre, normally aspirated model carried over from earlier years.

The new model is called "Speedster/VX220 Turbo".
